abstract: Representative Matt Gaetz of Florida said was possible that some of Mr. Trump’s closest supporters would instead serve in a “consultant” role.
lead_paragraph: Representative Matt Gaetz of Florida, a Republican and close ally of President Trump, cast doubt on the prospect of any House Republicans being named to the official defense team for the Senate trial, telling reporters it was possible that some of Mr. Trump’s closest supporters on Capitol Hill would instead serve in a “consultant” role.
